ORANGE COUNTY NEWSWATCH 
LIMELIGHT: The Rev. Louis Sheldon, Anaheim's "traditional values" crusader, is 
being shadowed by a CBS News crew this week as he lobbies in Sacramento. . . . 
He'll be included in a "48 Hours" program in June examining gay rights and its 
opponents. . . . "48 Hours" is a step up from the clamor of his recent 
"Donahue" appearance, Sheldon says. This time, he promises, "you'll see the 
real Lou Sheldon." Kris Lindgren and Dean Takahashi 
